OL,3,CUnion calls for action to save jobs
OL,4,Cafter Alstom stops production in Derby
OL,6,FUnion leaders have made urgent calls
OL,7,Ffor help to secure thousands of jobs
OL,8,Fat the UK's biggest rail assembly site
OL,9,Fafter production lines stopped because
OL,10,Fof a lack of orders.
OL,12,Fafter 10 months of discussions with
OL,13,Fthe Government over work for its Derby
OL,14,Fsite, it had run out of time.
OL,16,FSharon Graham said: "Unite will not
OL,17,Fstand by while the Government puts
OL,18,Fthousands of jobs at risk.
OL,26,@xD@UOU
