OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F377A1712005080
OL,3,CUnion calls for action to save jobs
OL,4,Cafter Alstom stops production in Derby
OL,6,F"There is a huge amount of work that
OL,7,FAlstom could and should be bidding
OL,8,Ffor, but the Government are simply not
OL,9,Ftendering for it and do not seem to
OL,10,Fcare.
OL,12,F"Alstom and the Government now need to
OL,13,Fstop endlessly procrastinating and
OL,14,Fjust get on and sign the contracts to
OL,15,Fensure the security of thousands of
OL,16,Fhighly skilled workers.
OL,18,F"If their inaction does lead to job
OL,19,Fcuts, the responsible people will be
OL,20,Fheld to account personally."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
