OL,3,CUnion calls for action to save jobs
OL,4,Cafter Alstom stops production in Derby
OL,6,FUnite regional secretary Paresh Patel
OL,7,Fadded: "Less talk and more action from
OL,8,Fboth Alstom and the Government is
OL,9,Fneeded to secure Alstom Rail in Derby.
OL,11,F"They both need to get their heads
OL,12,Ftogether to secure Derby rail and the
OL,13,Fthousands of jobs dependent upon this
OL,14,Femployer.
OL,16,F"Our members have had enough of quick
OL,17,Fsound bites and jam tomorrow ` there
OL,18,Fis a deal on the table that can and
OL,19,Fmust be secured.
