OL,3,CUnion calls for action to save jobs
OL,4,Cafter Alstom stops production in Derby
OL,6,F"Thousands of jobs depend upon it and
OL,7,Fboth the national and regional
OL,8,Feconomies will benefit from it."
OL,10,FA spokesperson for Alstom said: "We
OL,11,Fhave worked constructively with the
OL,12,FGovernment on securing a sustainable
OL,13,Ffuture for Derby Litchurch Lane, but
OL,14,Fafter 10 months of discussions we have
OL,15,Frun out of time, and the production
OL,16,Flines have stopped.
OL,18,F"We will now consult with our staff,
OL,19,Fwith trades unions and with our UK
OL,20,Fsupply chain to provide as much
OL,21,Fcertainty as we can."
