OL,3,CUnion calls for action to save jobs
OL,4,Cafter Alstom stops production in Derby
OL,6,FShadow transport secretary Louise
OL,7,FHaigh, said: "This news will be
OL,8,Fdevastating for Alstom employees, for
OL,9,FDerby, and for Britain's rail industry.
OL,11,F"The Transport Secretary has had
OL,12,Fmonths to find a solution to prevent
OL,13,Fthese job losses.
OL,15,F"It is clear he has failed to treat
OL,16,Fthis situation with the urgency it
OL,17,Fdeserves and has questions to answer
OL,18,Fon why he has failed to deliver on
OL,19,Fagreements to act to plug gaps in
OL,20,Forder schedules.
OL,26,@oD@NOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
