OL,3,CUnion calls for action to save jobs
OL,4,Cafter Alstom stops production in Derby
OL,6,F"Our rail industry needs certainty,
OL,7,Fstability and leadership; under this
OL,8,FConservative Government it has had
OL,9,Fnone of these things, and avoidable
OL,10,Fjob losses are the result.
OL,12,F"Britain was the country that created
OL,13,Fthe railways, but that legacy is being
OL,14,Ftrashed by a Conservative Government
OL,15,Fthat is content to oversee its managed
OL,16,Fdecline."
OL,18,FThe site employs around 3,000 people
OL,19,Fdirectly, with thousands more at risk
OL,20,Fin supply chains.
