OL,3,CUnion calls for action to save jobs
OL,4,Cafter Alstom stops production in Derby
OL,6,FA Department for Transport
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Rail manufacturing
OL,8,Fplays an important role in growing the
OL,9,FUK economy and delivering better
OL,10,Fservices for passengers.
OL,12,F"The Government is committed to
OL,13,Fsupporting the entire sector and we
OL,14,Fremain in close contact with Alstom to
OL,15,Fsecure a sustainable future for rail
OL,16,Fmanufacturing at Derby."
